metadata.name: CultPunk #1
metadata.description:
CultPunks are the first NFT collection on CULT DAO's zkEVM network, the Modulus blockchain.
The NFTs are 24x24 pixel art images, generated algorithmically, and the proceeds from the sale are being used to fund SoupSea which is the first NFT marketplace on the network.
Each Punk provides its owner with rights to a share of SoupSea's platform fees, effectively enabling automatic distributions from each and every transaction on the marketplace.
